name: mhzrsh dream gatherer (flux)
description:
The dreamgatherer cyles the thought formations into void. It renews and re-directs all dimensions into new possibilities and structures that will be born from chaos. Into its core, slow bursts of multiple soft texture and color parts fusion into a luminous mass. It moves and creates traces upon spreading its particles. It pulls in and out all parts to a multiple channel. 

Exclusive airdrop piece, sent to collectors of the year of 2021.
2480 x 3508 JPG dream scroll.
